
Vermin MUD:

== Initialization ==
Run: org.vermin.driver.BootstrapDatabase <driverclass> <jdbcurl> to create database
tables.
Example: java -cp build:derby.jar org.vermin.driver.BootstrapDatabase org.apache.derby.jdbc.EmbeddedDriver "jdbc:derby:database;create=true"

== Running the game ==
Run the main class org.vermin.mudlib.Main with the config file name as parameter.
Example: java -cp build:derby.jar:libs/jscheme.jar org.vermin.mudlib.Main config

== Logging in ==
Telnet to the port configured in config and use 'n' command to create a new character.

